Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When watching Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sora Naegino.\NI came to America all by myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with aspirations of joining Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is new to me, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm doing my best in the spirit\Nof "try it rather than think about it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can't do if I try,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if I can do it without\Ntrying, that'll be super lucky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I'm gonna do it, I just\Ngotta do it! Gotta! Gotta! That's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, everyone, are\Nyou really able to tell your feelings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to your mom and dad? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stuff like, "This is what I want to do."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, I know I shouldn't\Nmake my parents worry,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I don't want to have any regrets, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to tell them how \NI really feel, you know?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know? You know?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you want to do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time I was asked that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I looked up at the blue sky {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is only in my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't easily say the\Nwords that are really important{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I start running towards\Nthe place the light points to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's so much in my heart\Nthat I want to embrace, I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:02:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll keep painting my way,\NI promise, take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon,\Nwhere the white clouds drift{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future is lined up and\Nit'll always be there by my side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"My Amazingly Distant Family."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curtain rises in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, how did your grandma's surgery go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called me a little while\Nago and said it was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to give it our best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I'm doing something funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like my mind's going to go blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unlike us, Sora's already \Nhad stage experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's calm and composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The false appearance that deceives the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Did you have to go that far?! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}-She's still the same inside. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, where is Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in luck. Today's the day the\Nworld-famous star from Japan, Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will appear on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa... Papa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The surprises are yet to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have just a few more\Nminutes until the show starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this time to say your fond\Nfarewells to your humdrum daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to make sure\Nwe don't make any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seats are packed. Break a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Packed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Did I make you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as a performance\Nthat will not make you nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never realized. Even \NMiss Layla gets nervous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that you\Nguys are just barely passable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to go to the\Ntrouble of driving me there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora and I are friends.\NLet me do this for you, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla truly is good. She's so composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she's been through\Nlots of opening days already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's even livelier than she is at practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being good during the real\Nthing is what makes you a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Miss Sarah's song ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be time for you fairy\Ngodmothers to go on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done everything we\Ncan to be ready for this. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be confident. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And keep in time with each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, it's finally the scene\Nwhere we cast the spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Triple Illusion that we\Nworked our hardest to get right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! I was late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the smoke and flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla ad-libbed to cover for us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no. Smile, smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I made a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think the audience will\Naccept that kind of excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I'm sorry. I'm more to blame than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's my fault for\Nnot being able to respond
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Miss Layla's ad-lib at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you have a guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's... dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think he came to take Sora back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was against her joining\NKaleido Stage, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dad, this is Mia and Anna;\Nwe joined at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being friends with Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you let me know you were coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I came here on\Nshort notice because of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, this is Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you. Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to \Nsee me on stage today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you saw me\Nin an awkward situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just bumped into something during practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to stay here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could show you around, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know. Why don't we go\Nto the hotel restaurant tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have a Japanese meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... But I'm supposed to\Npractice with Mia and Anna, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:09:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but come to think of it, I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had Japanese in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll say goodbye here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dad! Come to see me tomorrow too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your current parents are \Nnot your real parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora, I think my hair got caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad came all this way to see me,\Nso I'm going to do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just totally unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about? It wasn't very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a review of yesterday's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In Kaleido Stage's new production,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla's big performance\Ndrew the audience's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the idea of the fairy\Ngodmother being played by a trio,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but their mistakes stood out and\Ntheir performance was also dull."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having that kinda of\Ncritique written about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's audience members have\Nprobably read that, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, let's pull ourselves\Ntogether and do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, being\Naffected by a newspaper critique?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch, I will cover for\Nany mistakes that you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both Mia and Anna's jumps\Nare smaller than yesterday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, those fairy godmothers are the ones
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the newspaper wrote a \Nterrible review of, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they are. I feel sorry for Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Mr. Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you three doing?!\NIf you're going to perform like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,step down from the stage right this minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is an important\Nscene where the spell is cast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they have the\Nnerve to appear on stage like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,\NI came to see how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom is also worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants me to bring you home\Nif you seem to be having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have opposed it more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you started telling me that\Nyou wanted to join Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have stopped you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a dangerous job...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't want to see\Nyou struggle any more than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not leaving for Japan until\Nyou say that you're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came looking for you,\Nsince you were out for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry for making you guys worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did your dad say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me... to come back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you aren't going home, are you? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go home!\NBut I couldn't say that to my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, we'll be your mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back before I was in grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my real mom and dad\Nwere killed in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My current dad is my real dad's cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he's not your real dad\Nthat he's telling you to come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ignoring your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and Dad both raised \Nme with a lot of care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I really love them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I couldn't tell him\Nthat I didn't want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just tell\Nhim your honest feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! Something terrible \Nhappened! Your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said your dad collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a call from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad was apparently\Ntaken to Cape Mary Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do? The evening\Nshow's going to start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to be on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll end up being absent for the performance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They may not forgive me for that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla might be able to get\Non stage as usual in this situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even though they may say\NI'm not being professional, for me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry\Nabout. Just let him rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think maybe I will go \Nback to Japan with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd stay near \Nyou and Mom after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that girl thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, her dad was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what reason she might have!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need a substitute for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do the show with\Njust two fairy godmothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla, cover for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can get\Naway with it by apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to quit Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you could be\Nclever and live your life that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me, right, Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should really think \Nit over one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I've already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't play that part without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late. Let's go\Napologize to the Boss right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that part even without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the only child Mom and Dad have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun getting to \Nperform in Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it was only for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Moon. Wavering emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when the clouds clear,\Nyour indecision will also vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't need to stay\Nin the hospital here a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you told me that you\Nwould come home, I got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time\Nyou saw Kaleido Stage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it? Did you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Miss Layla amazing? Mr. Yuri too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I got to be\Non stage with those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you said I could go to the audition,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I told you that I'd been accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you said, "Congratulations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I knew that you and\NMom were actually against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when you came to\Nsee me, I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've shown you\Na better performance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't\Nwant to quit Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to make\Nyou and Mom worry, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I'll go home by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it gets tough, you can\Ncome home whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our precious daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful not to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I told you yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just love Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.51,0:21:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let me try one more time. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not the ones you need to apologize to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're greatly indebted to the\Naudience who came to see the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them your best performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I want to be\Nable to tell my mom and dad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to come to see my\Nperformance with confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I'll be able to. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, what do you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never say you don't get any of that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sleep, play, flip through a magazine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, you're lonely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like always, invisible vibes fly\Naround the city today, tulututu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, the vector of my heart\Nis talking about so many reasons{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:23:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be free and fly the skies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't have space to spread my wings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have faith {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is a future yet to be shaped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there's a me that I want to shape{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I'm sad, even if it's a mistake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do what I want and\Nfly towards the freedom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:36.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I brought home a seal. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His name is Jonathan! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I heard we're not\Nallowed to keep any pets here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You say you'll take care of it yourself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but there's the cost of feeding him too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! In that case, the three\Nof us will enter a juggling contest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and aim for victory. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"The Amazing Seal."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.03,0:24:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
